statements: SELECT * FROM influencer_partnerships;
SELECT influencer_name, company_name, campaign_name FROM influencer_partnerships;
SELECT * FROM influencer_partnerships WHERE company_name = 'ABC Corp';
SELECT influencer_name, start_date, end_date FROM influencer_partnerships ORDER BY start_date DESC;
SELECT COUNT(id) AS total_campaigns FROM influencer_partnerships WHERE campaign_type = 'Social Media';
SELECT * FROM influencer_partnerships WHERE company_name = 'Company A' ORDER BY start_date DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT influencer_name, campaign_name, start_date, end_date FROM influencer_partnerships WHERE start_date > '2022-01-01' AND end_date < '2022-12-31'
SELECT DISTINCT company_name FROM influencer_partnerships WHERE campaign_type = 'Sponsored Post' ORDER BY company_name
SELECT influencer_name, company_name, campaign_name FROM influencer_partnerships WHERE influencer_name LIKE 'J%' AND campaign_name IS NOT NULL
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_campaigns, campaign_type FROM influencer_partnerships GROUP BY campaign_type HAVING total_campaigns > 2 ORDER BY total_campaigns DESC
SELECT influencer_name, followers_count FROM influencers
SELECT influencer_name, influencer_email FROM influencers WHERE followers_count > 10000
SELECT * FROM influencers ORDER BY influencer_name DESC
SELECT influencer_name, influencer_email, followers_count FROM influencers WHERE followers_count < 5000 ORDER BY followers_count ASC
SELECT campaign_name, campaign_type, start_date FROM campaigns ORDER BY start_date
SELECT * FROM influencers WHERE followers_count > 100 ORDER BY influencer_name ASC
SELECT influencer_name, followers_count FROM influencers WHERE influencer_email LIKE '%gmail.com'
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_campaigns FROM campaigns WHERE start_date <= '2022-01-01' AND end_date >= '2022-12-31'
SELECT campaign_name, campaign_type FROM campaigns WHERE campaign_type = 'Social Media' ORDER BY start_date DESC
SELECT influencer_name, followers_count FROM influencers JOIN campaigns ON influencers.influencer_id = campaigns.campaign_id
SELECT * FROM influencer;
SELECT name, followers FROM influencer WHERE id = 1;
SELECT influencer.name, partnership.brand_name FROM influencer JOIN partnership ON influencer.id = partnership.influencer_id;
SELECT campaign_name, campaign_start_date, campaign_end_date FROM campaign WHERE partnership_id = 2;
SELECT * FROM partnership WHERE contract_start_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM influencer WHERE followers > 1000;
SELECT name, followers FROM influencer ORDER BY followers DESC;
SELECT i.name AS influencer_name, p.brand_name AS brand_name FROM influencer AS i INNER JOIN partnership AS p ON i.id = p.influencer_id;
SELECT * FROM campaign WHERE campaign_end_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT i.name AS influencer_name, c.campaign_name AS campaign_name FROM influencer AS i INNER JOIN partnership AS p ON i.id = p.influencer_id INNER JOIN campaign AS c ON p.id = c.partnership_id;
SELECT id, name, followers FROM influencer WHERE followers > 1000 ORDER BY followers DESC;
SELECT name, start_date, end_date FROM campaign WHERE end_date > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY start_date DESC;
SELECT name, payment FROM partnership WHERE payment > 500 ORDER BY payment;
SELECT id, campaign_id, influencer_id, engagement_rate FROM collaboration WHERE engagement_rate > 5 ORDER BY engagement_rate DESC;
SELECT id, name FROM campaign WHERE start_date < '2022-05-01' ORDER BY start_date;
SELECT id, name, followers FROM influencer WHERE followers > 10000;
SELECT name, start_date, end_date FROM campaign WHERE start_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31';
SELECT id, influencer.name, campaign.name, payment FROM partnership INNER JOIN influencer ON partnership.influencer_id = influencer.id INNER JOIN campaign ON partnership.campaign_id = campaign.id;

SELECT campaign.name, influencer.name, engagement_rate FROM collaboration INNER JOIN campaign ON collaboration.campaign_id = campaign.id INNER JOIN influencer ON collaboration.influencer_id = influencer.id WHERE engagement_rate > 0.05 ORDER BY engagement_rate DESC;

SELECT influencer.name, COUNT(partnership.id) AS partnership_count FROM influencer LEFT JOIN partnership ON influencer.id = partnership.influencer_id GROUP BY influencer.name HAVING partnership_count > 5 ORDER BY partnership_count DESC;
SELECT * FROM influencers;
SELECT influencer_name, followers_count FROM influencers WHERE followers_count > 10000;
SELECT campaign_name, campaign_start_date FROM campaigns ORDER BY campaign_start_date DESC;
SELECT influencer_name, request_status FROM influencers JOIN collaboration_requests ON influencers.influencer_id = collaboration_requests.influencer_id WHERE request_status = 'approved';

SELECT influencer_name, campaign_name, collaboration_date FROM collaboration_history JOIN influencers ON collaboration_history.influencer_id = influencers.influencer_id JOIN campaigns ON collaboration_history.campaign_id = campaigns.campaign_id ORDER BY collaboration_date ASC;
SELECT * FROM influencers WHERE followers_count > 1000 ORDER BY influencer_name DESC
SELECT influencer_name, influencer_email FROM influencers WHERE influencer_id = 5
SELECT campaign_name, campaign_start_date, campaign_end_date FROM campaigns WHERE campaign_id = 3
SELECT influencer_name, followers_count, p.partnership_type FROM influencers i JOIN partnerships p ON i.influencer_id = p.influencer_id WHERE p.campaign_id = 2

SELECT c.campaign_name, i.influencer_name, ch.collaboration_date FROM collaborations c JOIN influencers i ON c.influencer_id = i.influencer_id JOIN collaboration_history ch ON c.campaign_id = ch.campaign_id WHERE ch.engagement_level = 'High' ORDER BY ch.collaboration_date DESC
